<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20102000">“热恋中女人的迷人可爱，而长期相处后这些吸引男人注意到她的那些品质都消失不见了。”这句话说的对么？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="220822" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">MS出自某电视剧</div>


</div>
