<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$zengjuchen"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/zengjuchen">
<img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/5acfa84d9_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="http://pic2.zhimg.com/5acfa84d9_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$zengjuchen" href="/people/zengjuchen">曾举臣</a>，<strong title="A little knowledge is a dangerous thing." class="zu-question-my-bio">A little knowledge is a dangerous thing.</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="3">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zeepen" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zeepen" class="zg-link" title="Zeepen">Zeepen</a></span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
